    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Strengthen and scale up on site and community based PMTCT and Paediatric HIV and AIDS services. \r\nConduct relevant studies in the area of PMTCT service utilization by MARP, MARAs and EVAs; and  stigma & discrimination to HIV positive pregnant women.\r\nProvide technical support for developing next NSP; integrating PMTCT and Paediatric HIV and AIDS services in the government MNH and IMCI services; reviewing ad revising HIV and AIDS policy,  VCT guidelines; developing and finalizing EID guidelines as well as other relevant policies and documents\r\nProvide technical assistance for developing and implementing a social mobilization and community sensitization package on stigma and discrimination as well as support for MARAs and EVAs to access HIV services\r\nMonitor the programme implementation from both quantitative and qualitative aspect.\r\n(In 2008 – 2010 CPAP, the funds were managed based on the projects whereas the funds for 2011-2012 has been allocated based on the IRs. Therefore, the budget in this AID management platform is reflected only for 2011-2012)."
      },
      "ne": null
    },
